scopecontent.p:
Volumes containing meeting minutes (1833-1837), constitution, membership lists
				(1830-1897); confession of faith adopted 1847, list of members (1847-1867), minutes
				of board meetings, accounts of special services and meeting minutes (1847-1872);
				constitution and amendments as of April 1892, with list of members and non-members;
				a parish and church record book compiled July 1892 with entries up to 1953; and the
				Evangelical Magazine and Gospel Advocate, Vol. III, 1836.
